  "title": "Waiter/Waitress S$2800 to S$3200.",
  "description": "<p>Are you passionate about providing exceptional service and creating memorable dining experiences?</p><p>Rosso Vino is looking for enthusiastic individuals to join our team as waiters/waitresses!</p><p><br /></p><p>Highlights:</p><ul><li>Singaporean or PR</li><li>Salary ranging from S$2800 to S$3200 in basic pay</li><li>Two staff meals are provided per day</li><li>Transportation provided after 11 pm</li><li>High tips and additional incentives</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>If you're ready to embark on a rewarding career journey and contribute to the success of Rosso Vino, apply now! Join us in creating unforgettable dining experiences and become a valued member of our dynamic team. Apply today and take the first step towards an exciting career in hospitality!</p>",
